				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/A-Ph%C3%B2ng-cung-ph%C3%BA/poem-PRU_ew2Q9_CUGXM-oZrryg">A Phòng cung phú - 阿房宮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/B%E1%BA%A1ch-S%C6%A1n-tr%C3%A0/poem-c5IqahtmUeLQ5z2JFI49BQ">Bạch Sơn trà - 白山茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Ch%C3%ADnh-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BA%A5t-nh%E1%BA%ADt-di-t%E1%BB%91ng-Th%E1%BB%ABa-Thi%C3%AAn-ng%E1%BB%A5c-to%E1%BA%A3-c%E1%BA%A5m/poem-TPul1DvfCm5PaDZjUBX75Q">Chính nguyệt nhị thập nhất nhật di tống Thừa Thiên ngục toả cấm - 正月二十一日移送承天獄鎖禁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Tri%E1%BB%81u/Chu-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc/poem-ZabFFWnuAZnhAkkau9ZkSA">Chu trung độc chước - 舟中獨酌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Tri%E1%BB%81u/author-0-sb0Y9_iaj8YxIytSFQ8A">Trần Quang Triều</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ch%E1%BB%A7ng-oa-c%E1%BB%B1/poem-OmZprMrp6Q98cV47zLioSA">Chủng oa cự - 種萵苣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/%C4%90%C4%83ng-Ng%C5%A9-H%C3%A0nh-s%C6%A1n-l%C6%B0u-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-TeV8EoYOaFh3R-8VihEYfg">Đăng Ngũ Hành sơn lưu đề - 登五行山留題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thi